- **Application Code:** `next-app/src/`
- **Components:** `next-app/src/components/`
- **Database:** `next-app/src/db/`
- **Actions:** `next-app/src/lib/actions/`
- **Pages:** `next-app/src/app/`
- **Config Files:** `next-app/` (package.json, next.config.ts, etc.)